Title: Pincers and Needles
Description:
We've been running low on needles for tailoring lately. Those darn things keep snapping in two!

Some pointy parts from the scythid in the area might serve as good replacements.
ObjectivesText: Gather 10 Pointy Pincers from the scythid of the Dragon Isles for Gnoklin Quirkcoil of the Dragonscale Expedition.
